{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be rustic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evergreen Threads</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f5e6e0; /* A soft, natural off-white */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #8b0000; /* Deep Red */\n            color: #f5e6e0;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #5a0000; /* Darker red for accent */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            background-color: #a00000; /* Slightly lighter red */\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #f5e6e0;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #d0a0a0; /* A muted red for hover */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #8b0000;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #a00000;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #8b0000;\n            color: #f5e6e0;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            color: #f5e6e0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .products {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .product-item {\n            border: 1px solid #d0a0a0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            background-color: #fefaf8;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .product-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .product-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .product-item h3 {\n            color: #8b0000;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .product-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #a00000;\n            color: #f5e6e0;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #8b0000;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            background-color: #5a0000;\n            color: #f5e6e0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Evergreen Threads</h1>\n        <p>Timeless Style, Consciously Crafted</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">Our Story</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Shop</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Embrace Sustainable Luxury</h2>\n        <p>Discover our collection of beautifully crafted garments made from organic and recycled materials. Fashion that feels good and does good.</p>\n        <a href=\"#products\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Collection</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>Our Story</h2>\n            <p>At Evergreen Threads, we believe in fashion that respects both people and the planet. Our journey began with a passion for creating elegant, durable clothing that minimizes environmental impact. We meticulously source sustainable fabrics like organic cotton, linen, and recycled textiles, and partner with ethical manufacturers who share our values. Every piece is designed to be a timeless addition to your wardrobe, transcending fleeting trends.</p>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x300/d0a0a0/ffffff?text=Sustainable+Fabric+Image\" alt=\"Sustainable fabric close-up\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px;\">\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"products\">\n            <h2>Our Latest Collection</h2>\n            <div class=\"products\">\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/8b0000/ffffff?text=Linen+Dress\" alt=\"Linen Dress\">\n                    <h3>Organic Linen Dress</h3>\n                    <p>A flowing, breathable dress perfect for any occasion. Made from 100% GOTS certified organic linen.</p>\n                    <p><strong>$120.00</strong></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/a00000/ffffff?text=Recycled+Tee\" alt=\"Recycled T-Shirt\">\n                    <h3>Recycled Cotton Tee</h3>\n                    <p>Soft and comfortable, this essential tee is crafted from recycled cotton fibers.</p>\n                    <p><strong>$55.00</strong></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/5a0000/ffffff?text=Hemp+Pants\" alt=\"Hemp Pants\">\n                    <h3>Hemp Blend Trousers</h3>\n                    <p>Durable and naturally anti-microbial, these trousers offer style and sustainability.</p>\n                    <p><strong>$95.00</strong></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View All Products</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <p>We'd love to hear from you! For inquiries, custom orders, or just to say hello, reach out to us.</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@evergreenthreads.com\" style=\"color: #8b0000;\">info@evergreenthreads.com</a></p>\n            <p>Follow us on Instagram: <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: #8b0000;\">@EvergreenThreads</a></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Evergreen Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll to section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}